    <h2>Coal Mine</h2>
    <p>Flips when all coal cubes are removed. Coal must be transported via links.</p>
    <table class="wiki-table">
      <tr><th>Level</th><th>Cost</th><th>Iron</th><th>Cubes</th><th>Income</th><th>VP</th></tr>
      <tr><td>1</td><td>£5</td><td>0</td><td>2</td><td>+4</td><td>1</td></tr>
      <tr><td>2</td><td>£7</td><td>0</td><td>3</td><td>+7</td><td>2</td></tr>
      <tr><td>3</td><td>£8</td><td>1</td><td>4</td><td>+6</td><td>3</td></tr>
      <tr><td>4</td><td>£10</td><td>1</td><td>5</td><td>+5</td><td>4</td></tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Iron Works</h2>
    <p>Flips when all iron cubes are removed. Iron can be used from anywhere (no transport).</p>
    <table class="wiki-table">
      <tr><th>Level</th><th>Cost</th><th>Coal</th><th>Cubes</th><th>Income</th><th>VP</th></tr>
