      <tr><td>4</td><td>£12</td><td>1</td><td>6</td><td>+1</td><td>9</td></tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Port</h2>
    <p>Flips when used to sell cotton. Also enables access to external/distant markets.</p>
    <table class="wiki-table">
      <tr><th>Level</th><th>Cost</th><th>Income</th><th>VP</th></tr>
      <tr><td>1</td><td>£9</td><td>+3</td><td>2</td></tr>
      <tr><td>2</td><td>£12</td><td>+3</td><td>4</td></tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Shipyard</h2>
    <p>Flips immediately when built. High VP but requires developing through lower levels and specific locations.</p>
    <table class="wiki-table">
      <tr><th>Level</th><th>Cost</th><th>Coal</th><th>Iron</th><th>Income</th><th>VP</th><th>Era</th></tr>
